title: 083: Farfetch’d
author: Chris Taylor
description:
Farfetch’d loves leeks, or magical sticks, or we don’t really know but it made for a real story! Check it out in Episode 83 of Magmar Sucks the ranking of Pokemon.

Hosts: [Chris](https://twitter.com/DaLiquidSword), [Mark](https://www.twitch.tv/robobobatron), [Aleksandar](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC56emXYp1pHXL2E9SLcYisw), [Ethan](https://twitter.com/synspawn)

For more episodes and the full ranking list visit [Magmar Sucks](http://www.magmarsucks.com) on the web.

For more on the Pokemon in this episode check out their [Bulbapedia page](http://bulbapedia.bulbagarden.net/wiki/Farfetch'd)
